'''Christiaan Justus Enschedé ''' (9 December 1788 in [[Haarlem]] &ndash;26 June 1829 in Haarlem) was a Haarlem newspaper editor and printer.

==Biography==
He was a son of [[Johannes Enschedé Jr.]] and [[Johanna Elisabeth Swaving]]. For some time he was a partner in the [[Joh. Enschedé|family company]]. On 9 August 1827 in [[Rotterdam]] he married Adriana Maria van Dalen (Rotterdam, 10 May 1801 &ndash; Haarlem, 31 January 1858) the daughter of Abraham Cornelis Dalen and Jacoba Catharina Durselen.

